  {
    "key": "dac9ec98fab5f6ad0ab915511b14ae7fb086a6aa3a51c43181fe53b8cc9bf431",
    "original": "Imagine the trail of terror we could blaze if your skills matched your bravery.\nWe shall train five men to master their weapons so that they may act as a vanguard!",
